3. Features of Python :
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
A. Simple and easy to learn : Just like English language.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
B. Freeware and open source : Code is available for anyone.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
C. High Level Programming Language : Don't need to worry about much things.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
D. Platform Independent : Same code can work on any OS or Browser.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
E. Portability : I don't really understand it. Lmao.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
F. Dynamically Typed : Huh.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
G. POP & OOP : Have both the POP & OOP Features.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
H. Interpreted : Just Runtime. Line by Line execution.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
I. Extensible : Can use Java or C code inside it's application if there is a need of 
performance or security respectively.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
J. Embedded : We can embed Python code into any other programming language.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
K. Extensive Library : Huge Ass Libraries.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------